    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Garuda Indonesia\nTimetable\nU.S.A Edition\nApril 1st, 1991 to\nOctober 27st, 1991\nVISIT\nINDONESIA\nYEAR 1991",
      "We're a lot bigger\nthan most travelers think.\nGaruda Indonesia, serving 4\ncontinents and 23 countries\nfor more than forty years, is\nthe largest airline in the\nSouthern Hemisphere.\nLAKE TOBA\nSUMATRA\nKALIMANTAN\nBALIKPAPAN\nSULAWES\n• TORAJALAN\nJAKARTA\nJAVA\nSIRARAYA\nJUNG PANDA\n- ABU DHABI\nADELAIDE\n- AMSTERDAM\nAUCKLAND\n- BANGKOK\nBRISBANE\nBRUSSELS\nBALI\n• BIAK\n• DARWIN\nFUKUOKA\nFRANKFURT\n- HO CHI MINH\n- HONG KONG\n- HONOLULU\n- JAKARTA\n- JEDDAH\n- KUALA LUMPUR\n-- LONDON\nLOS ANGELÉS\n-— MANILA\n- MELBOURNE\n- MENADO\n- NAGOYA\n- PARIS\nPERTH\nPORT HEDLAND\n•- RIYADH\n- ROME\nSEOUL\n- SINGAPORE\n- SYDNEY\n- VIENNA\nZURICH\nGaruda Indonesia"
    ],
